{"tid":332223,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"歷代火影邊個最偉大？","createTime":"2017-07-22T21:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T03:19:25.000Z","uid":5190,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16313f459683f2d74eeeac5d9787225c7115dc50","tid":332223,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:49:44.000Z","msg":"我相信好多人都會覺得係第一代<br />\n佢建立起木葉 制止左班 封印左九尾 幾乎係歷代最強火影<br />\n<br />\n但係我眼中 無人及得上波風水門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣對付住九尾 佢實力可以話差一代成大截 但佢堅持火影嘅職責 甚麼犧牲自己 都要封印九尾<br />\n<br />\n攞起戰衣 就要踏上不歸路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/054319_5a57ea95326a6989abd1ce0e1040debc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F23%2F054319_5a57ea95326a6989abd1ce0e1040debc.jpg&h=c4ff0a37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f293190b7a7d12e92bfcefad12b7aaf6d24fe90","tid":332223,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T21:51:20.000Z","msg":"都係一、四啦<br />\n二都ok... 幫一代執屎<br />\n鳴仔更加唔使講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fc50545a8d75f37909c01b2d9bcc70a7b98137","tid":332223,"uid":4210,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T22:23:05.000Z","msg":"至少一定唔會係你囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6a03d4a19da5b7e52b0d68d81496b3425c84a7","tid":332223,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T23:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我相信好多人都會覺得係第一代<br />\n佢建立起木葉 制止左班 封印左九尾 幾乎係歷代最強火影<br />\n<br />\n但係我眼中 無人及得上波風水門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同樣對付住九尾 佢實力可以話差一代成大截 但佢堅持火影嘅職責 甚麼犧牲自己 都要封印九尾<br />\n<br />\n攞起戰衣 就要踏上不歸路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/23/054319_5a57ea9532